These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: cola, lemonade
Movie-Genre: sports, disaster
Sport: tennis, skiing
Transport: skateboard, helicopter
1. Transport:helicopter is on the left or right of Sport:skiing##3
2. Beverage:lemonade is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:disaster == Beverage:cola##1
4. Transport:helicopter is on the right of Transport:skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | cola  | lemonade   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | sports   |
| Sport         | skiing | tennis |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: pumpkin, watermelon
Movie-Genre: zombie, crime
Pet: hedgehog, hamster
Transport: ship, bike
1. Pet:hamster is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:zombie == Transport:bike##1
3. Food:watermelon is on the right of Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | pumpkin     | watermelon |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | zombie  |
| Pet           | hamster         | hedgehog     |
| Transport     | ship   | bike    |

 #################################
 
