.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Job: scientist, entrepreneur
Nationality: chinese, polish
Pet: rat, snake
Sport: volleyball, tennis
1. Sport:tennis is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:polish is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:entrepreneur == Nationality:chinese##1
4. Pet:rat is on the left of Nationality:polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | scientist    |
| Nationality   | chinese       | polish |
| Pet           | rat         | snake    |
| Sport         | volleyball    | tennis   |

